<br>
For weapons, you'll be dual wielding soon so look at getting some cheap yet reasonably decent 1hand weapons .  At your level, ratio is more important than procs.  Go for something in the 10 damage 20 delay range, you probably won't get something quite that but it gives you something to shoot for.<br>
<br>
Don't worry about it too awfully much, not for many levels yet.  Its not until the 30s or 40s that things really start becoming important gear wise.<br>
<br>
As far as experience goes, Northern Ro and Oasis are good at that level, at least they were in the day.  Once you get into the mid to late teens though, many people recommend pauldron caverns.<br>
<br>
Having a Shaman partner will make outside adventuring much easier, since sow is a life saver.<br>
